<NEW>

There was a nod from ASTRA as she escorted WHEELIE out to where
approximately they had met. It was at that point she stopped.

Much of the scenery had changed. There was no hint of strange pyramid
that had housed the CORNU, the path was hidden and even the vegetation
had seemed to change somewhat, becoming more jungle-like again instead
of the forest they had been in before.

"This is where my journey ends." ASTRA said calmly and yet with a hint
of sadness. "I hope you find what you seek. We will take good care of
your friend." She waved as her imaged wavered for a moment and then
vanished from view leaving WHEELIE seemingly alone once more.

(TAG)

- Preston
